    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been well-loved over the years. It drives smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with it, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next big adventure with you. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable ride that won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
