      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a quintessential driver\u2019s machine, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The high-revving naturally aspirated engine delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a recent inspection of the rear subframe mounting points and refreshed bushings. Finished in Carbon Black, the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, but the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system components and valve clearances\u2014have been meticulously addressed. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber, offering exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
