      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, having been regularly waxed and garage-kept. Upon close inspection, you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of careful road use\u2014but the body panels are straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is supple, with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. All electronic components, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and heated seats, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it starts up immediately, idles quietly, and the transmission shifts through all gears with precision. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, a new engine air filter, and a brake pad replacement within the last 5,000 miles. This car is turn-key and ready for its next owner to enjoy for many miles to come.",
      "price": 34500.0,
