    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and I\u2019m so excited for it to find a new home! It\u2019s been a super reliable companion for me and is still in really solid shape. It runs smoothly, looks great, and has been well-loved and taken care of over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for many more adventures, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
