    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to address floor cracking, and the double-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated hub. The suspension geometry is maintained via fresh control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh (water pump, thermostat, and expansion tank). While the exterior exhibits minor stone chips and light bolster wear on the Nappa leather, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition with strong compression across all cylinders.",
